{
  "stem": "27770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Once in a while my father, who was inviting such a Polish Jew to Friday night, but the supper when we had Friday night, and this Jew was by us, he was shivering because if one goy would see that a Jew-- a Polish came into us, next day we would be finished.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they told us, the Polish people, what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one day in the [INAUDIBLE] comes a Polish guy and tells us you know what happened in Poland?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We says, what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, they took 200 Jews, they was put in a big room, and they were testing gas on them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I couldn't believe such a thing on human being to test gas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So and you don't want to believe it, and that's how human nature is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One talk to the other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The guy's a little mixed up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He's stupid.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you want to test gas, why you have to test them on a Jew?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You can test them on a dog.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, when we came to concentration camp, and we was chased with dogs that the Germans had like this, you mensch.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It means they called the dog the human being and us they called the dogs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he told the dog, you mensch-- actually dog-- [NON-ENGLISH]-- bite the dog.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The dog was the Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So those days we didn't understand such a thing there is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he probably knew more, and he wanted to explain us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't want to believe it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So actually it was not a testing from gas, they gassed people, because a bullet for each Jew to give was maybe a penny or two.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
